drivers: usb: core: hcd: Whitespace fixes

including
- spaces to tabs
- removing spaces before array indexing (foo [] to foo[])
- adding spaces around unary operator (foo? 1 : 0 to foo ? 1 : 0)
- removed trailing whitespace

